<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.5">
<l>pāṇṭēṉvaṇ ṭaṟaiyum kuḻalārkaḷpal lāṇṭicaippa</l>
<l>vāṇṭārvai yamellā maracākimuṉ ṉāṇṭavarē</l>
<l>māṇṭāreṉ ṟuvantā rantōmaṉaivāḻk kaitaṉṉai</l>
<l>vēṇṭēṉniṉ ṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Rulers who ruled previously, becoming kings of the whole world,</l>
<l>While those with curls, where honeybees hum melodies, sang</l>
<l rend="indent">“[May you live] many years,”</l>
<l>Came [only] that they [should] die. What a pity! I do not want a mundane life.</l>
<l>I take refuge in you, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
